### Accessibility

Add to the .stat-block elements:
  role="text"
  aria-label="[target][suffix] [label]"
  e.g. aria-label="13+ Systems powering the associate experience"

This way screen readers announce the complete stat without 
reading the animated intermediate numbers.

Also:
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .stat-block {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
    transition: none;
  }
  .stat-label {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
    transition: none;
  }
}

And in TypeScript, skip the animation:
  if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches) {
    el.textContent = target.toString();
    return;
  }

